{"_path":"/maps/_software/whale-fall/whale-fall","_dir":"whale-fall","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Whale Fall","description":"大型开源项目死亡后的生态演替，类比海洋中的鲸落现象","original_path":"content/6.maps/_software/whale-fall.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"开源项目的鲸落三阶段"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开源项目的鲸落三阶段"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当大型开源项目停止维护时，会像鲸尸一样经历三个生态阶段："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1. 移动食腐者"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：直接 fork 并接管项目"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OpenOffice → LibreOffice"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MySQL → MariaDB"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hudson → Jenkins"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2. 富集机会主义者"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：针对死项目的数据格式开发替代工具"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Google Reader 关闭后：Feedly、Miniflux、FreshRSS、Tiny Tiny RSS 等涌现，实现 Google Reader API 兼容"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"许可证无关紧要，接口公开且其他软件依赖它就足够"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3. 化能自养细菌"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：协议、文件格式、API 契约等结构骨架持续支持社区"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OpenDocument Format 超越了创建它的 OpenOffice"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Docker 将容器运行时捐给 OCI，Docker 自身衰落但规范永存"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tree-sitter 为 Atom 而建，Atom 归档后成为 Zed、Neovim、Helix 的语法引擎"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://nesbitt.io/2026/02/21/whale-fall.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Whale Fall - Andrew Nesbitt"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"连续再殖民化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"连续再殖民化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开源项目死亡后的典型模式：项目沉寂 → 有人 fork → 其他项目依赖该 fork → fork 维护者燃尽 → 循环重复，但规模逐代缩小，直到概念迁移而非代码继承。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sass 的迁移路径"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：Ruby gem → LibSass (C++) → Dart Sass。每代重写都受益于前代的 bug 报告和设计争论，但实现被抛弃。大多数写 Sass 的人不知道它始于 Ruby gem。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"失败模式"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：Edera 在 Rust tar-rs 库发现解析漏洞，影响所有下游 fork（async-tar、tokio-tar、Astral 内部 fork）。代码通过连续 fork 复制，但没人重新审计继承自原版的 PAX 头解析逻辑。安全漏洞就这样藏在骨架中，协调披露需要联系约二十个实体，其中多个库无人维护。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"许可证变更触发食腐"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"许可证变更触发食腐"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"项目从开源转向源码可用许可证时，食腐阶段几乎立即触发："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Redis → Valkey"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Elasticsearch → OpenSearch"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Terraform → OpenTofu"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"社区已形成固定流程： rush fork 最后一个开放提交 → 短暂竞争 → 整合到一两个幸存者。从开源生态视角看，代码主体已停止接受外部贡献。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持久的抽象层"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：集成项目面临选择——跟随专有版本或转向 fork，许多人选择构建兼容垫片。这些垫片往往在许可证争议冷却多年后，仍在依赖原版 API 的骨架生存。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"sun-microsystems-的鲸群死亡"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sun Microsystems 的鲸群死亡"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Oracle 2010 年收购 Sun 不是单一鲸落，而是整群鲸鱼同时死亡：Java、Solaris、ZFS、DTrace、VirtualBox、NetBeans、GlassFish、Hudson、MySQL。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每个都沉到各自的海底，产生不同的继承："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"单一主导 fork"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：Hudson→Jenkins、ZFS→OpenZFS"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多线竞争"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：MySQL 喂养出 MariaDB、Percona、Drizzle（后者本身又成为小鲸落）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基金会辗转"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：NetBeans→Apache、GlassFish→Payara 和 Jakarta EE"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"结构骨架（JVM 字节码格式、ZFS 磁盘格式、MySQL 协议）至今仍是负载-bearing，而许多开发者从未听说过 Sun。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"浅水区与云厂商整合"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"浅水区与云厂商整合"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"浅水区死亡"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：收购式招聘（acqui-hires）——公司被吸收，代码闭源或归档，知识随人员 disperses 而非积累为公共资源。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"云厂商整合趋势"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：当前大型开源项目被平台公司拥有的趋势正在减少鲸落率。这可能产生二阶效应——生态系统多样性受损，但无人追踪。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健康生态需要稳定的鲸落供应——尽管这意味着希望大型项目死亡，因为深海海底没有其他食物来源。"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_software:whale-fall:whale-fall.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_software/whale-fall/whale-fall.md","_stem":"6.maps/_software/whale-fall/whale-fall","_extension":"md"}